<c.japanese>&lrm;（火岩）うっ！
&lrm;（氷岩）うっ…</c.japanese>

204
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,087
<c.japanese>&lrm;（氷岩）あっ…</c.japanese>

205
00:11:11,712 --> 00:11:12,630
<c.japanese>&lrm;（火岩）うっ くっ…</c.japanese>

206
00:11:15,716 --> 00:11:17,134
<c.japanese>&lrm;ふっ…</c.japanese>

207
00:11:17,218 --> 00:11:18,803
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

208
00:11:18,886 --> 00:11:21,305
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

209
00:11:22,014 --> 00:11:23,140
<c.japanese>&lrm;どう思う？</c.japanese>

210
