<c.japanese>&lrm;何だ？</c.japanese>

238
00:12:34,587 --> 00:12:37,131
<c.japanese>&lrm;こ… こいつらは…</c.japanese>

239
00:12:37,214 --> 00:12:39,759
<c.japanese>&lrm;（神雲(じんうん)）ここには おらぬか</c.japanese>

240
