253
00:13:19,757 --> 00:13:22,176
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

254
00:13:22,259 --> 00:13:24,678
<c.japanese>&lrm;ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

255
