<c.japanese>&lrm;まさか 神雲様？</c.japanese>

264
00:13:46,158 --> 00:13:49,453
<c.japanese>&lrm;神雲？　あっ そういや そんな…</c.japanese>

265
00:13:49,537 --> 00:13:52,206
<c.japanese>&lrm;龍はダメだ 龍は…</c.japanese>

266
00:13:52,915 --> 00:13:54,375
<c.japanese>&lrm;逃げるぞ！</c.japanese>

267
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,968
<c.japanese>&lrm;はっ…</c.japanese>

268
00:14:04,802 --> 00:14:05,845
<c.japanese>&lrm;氷岩</c.japanese>

269
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:08,097
<c.japanese>&lrm;神雲様</c.japanese>

270
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:14,353
<c.japanese>&lrm;（神雲）幕府要人呪殺(じゅさつ)請負の咎(とが)で
&lrm;この場で抹殺処分とする</c.japanese>

271
00:14:14,436 --> 00:14:16,855
<c.japanese>&lrm;幕府要人呪殺？</c.japanese>

272
