<c.japanese>&lrm;千夜 未熟</c.japanese>

287
00:15:10,242 --> 00:15:11,660
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ…</c.japanese>

288
00:15:15,539 --> 00:15:18,500
<c.japanese>&lrm;申し訳ありません 神雲様</c.japanese>

289
00:15:19,501 --> 00:15:22,671
<c.japanese>&lrm;（神雲）よい 学んだな</c.japanese>

290
00:15:23,255 --> 00:15:25,174
<c.japanese>&lrm;氷岩も逃げたか</c.japanese>

291
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:29,762
<c.japanese>&lrm;まあ よい 長くは持つまい</c.japanese>

292
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:33,182
<c.japanese>&lrm;（真介）ハァ ハァ ハァ…</c.japanese>

293
00:15:33,265 --> 00:15:37,478
